summaries.short: Carlo breaks up a lovers' quarrel at a restaurant and the couple turn up at his office.
summaries.full: Carlo breaks up a lovers' quarrel at a restaurant and the couple turn up at his office looking for a 'cure' to their pattern of fighting in order to wind up in bed exploring shared sexual fantasies. The pair involve Carlo and his colleague Valentina in their dangerous games which go far beyond the consulting office.

summaries.short: A former patient returns to see Carlo after his wife passes away, trying to understand what he saw the moment she died.
summaries.full: A former patient returns to see Carlo after his wife passes away, trying to understand what he saw the moment she died, which he believes to be her soul departing from her body.

summaries.short: Carlo meets his stepson's girlfriend Janaína who Carlo believes is a cutter.
summaries.full: Carlo meets his stepson's girlfriend Janaína who Carlo believes is a cutter. After running into her at an art exhibit, Carlo insists on another meeting to get to the bottom of her self-mutilation and eventually she reveals her persistent desire to vanish without a trace.
